‘Many fair and favourite places are there on earth, none - that 1 love so fondly as Tibur. Do you Plancus, whether as now in camp or, as you will be soon, we trust, at Tibur, remember ,that it is occasionally true philosophy to forget care in wine? ‚Think of the example of Teucer in his troubles.’
